data.title: Orient MedNet Network List
data.meta_description: Orient MedNet Network List - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document lists information about various healthcare providers in Abu Dhabi, including their name, type, region, address, specialties, telephone number, and whether they participate in various insurance plans. A note at the top indicates that visiting doctors not following contractual rates at these providers will not be available for direct billing. The providers include hospitals, medical centers, and specialty clinics across Abu Dhabi.
